<!--Display Property Inline= same,line,fill the size of content,cant set width & height,Inline block= same,fill the size of the content we can set width & height
block= different line fill the size of entire wisth we can set height & width,none=this will hidethe element from the html-->
<style>h4{background-color: red;display: block;}
p{background-color: blueviolet;display: inline-block;height:100;width:100px;}
span{background-color: aquamarine;display:inline;height:500px;}</style>
